# Chiq U55H7C TV remote codes
## Volume up
```
Protocol=NEC Address=0x40 Command=0x1A Raw-Data=0xE51ABF40 32 bits LSB first
Send with: IrSender.sendNEC(0x40, 0x1A, <numberOfRepeats>);

Protocol=NEC Address=0x40 Command=0x1A Repeat gap=40400us
```

## Volume down
```
Protocol=NEC Address=0x40 Command=0x1E Raw-Data=0xE11EBF40 32 bits LSB first
Send with: IrSender.sendNEC(0x40, 0x1E, <numberOfRepeats>);

Protocol=NEC Address=0x40 Command=0x1E Repeat gap=40350us
```


## Mute
```
Protocol=NEC Address=0x40 Command=0x10 Raw-Data=0xEF10BF40 32 bits LSB first
Send with: IrSender.sendNEC(0x40, 0x10, <numberOfRepeats>);

Protocol=NEC Address=0x40 Command=0x10 Repeat gap=40400us
```
